properties.headline: CHANGED TRAFFIC CONDITIONS Technical fault - EWINGSDALE Pacific Highway off-ramp to Ewingsdale Road
properties.otherAdvice:
Due to a fault with the movable median.

Only the off-ramp is closed. Through traffic on the Pacific Hwy is not affected.
properties.diversions:
For access to Byron Bay

Light vehicles can use Kennedys Lane, Myocum Rd, Ewingsdale Rd.

Heavy vehicles should continue on Pacific Hwy southbound and take Lennox Head exit to Hinterland Way,  then continue south on Hinterland Way to Tamarind Dr at Tintenbar, then right onto Pacific Hwy northbound. Drivers can then use either Bangalow Rd or Ewingsdale Rd northbound exits for access to Byron Bay.
